class NA:
    def __init__(self, x: int):
        self.x = x

    def __str__(self):
        return f'NA({self.x})'

lista_preenchida: list[int] = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
lista_preencida_objetos: list[NA] = [NA(1), NA(2), NA(3), NA(4), NA(5)]

lista_preenchida.append(NA(6)) #remover do final
